products.title: Scandi Ferns Linen Thunder Roman Blind
products.description: Heres how you make a tonal palette bright and cheerful. The mix of greys and neutrals lend an earthy tone to the tightly packed leaf pattern, creating warmth amongst all that cool grey. The pattern itself is a thing of beauty, dense and layered, all sharply drawn and stylishl heres how you make a tonal palette bright and cheerful.
